Main Duties &amp; Responsibilities:
1. Full aspect of AP &amp; AR for multi set of entities (inclusive banks reconciliations)
2. Daily accounting entries and month end closing
3. Sound knowledge of local GST
4. Monitor daily cashflow and FD renewal
5. Prepare import and export LC for submission to bank and monitor trade financing to banks
6. Sorting of incoming finance mails
7. Staff claims processing
8. Perform ad-hoc duties as and when required

Job Requirements
1. Pro-active, committed and motivated individual who is meticulous, have an eye for detail, and enjoy working in a fast-paced dynamic environment
2. Good communication, analytical and interpersonal skills
3. Relevant accounting diploma and accounting work experience (1-2 years)
4. Working experience with accounting software systems is preferred
5. Good knowledge of Microsoft Office applications